    - target: {fileID: 3435467237574143893, guid: b6ff7e9fa6be6224db075a4f94c206ec, type: 3}
      propertyPath: journalFullText
      value: After trekking through the underground, I have finally reached the surface.
        It looks like there might be something buried beneath that wood over there.
        It would be ideal if there was some slime mold over there, but I can't see
        any... maybe if I could use my fan tool to blow some slime mold spores from
        this side over to the other side, into the shade under the bridge?
